married to her until we got rich...

00:37:03.721 --> 00:37:09.727
without being swayed by a dumb thing
like love and even have a baby...

00:37:10.728 --> 00:37:14.565
then child support
wouldn't be a problem now!

00:37:14.632 --> 00:37:16.067
